messages.messageBody:
Either people aren't posting or I'm not getting yahoo mail yet.

I rejoined the other list. I'm not going to stay to the point of abuse. But
even that list isn't coming in but a trickle.

It could be AOL has so much backed up yahoo mail it's going to be a while, or
maybe we just won't get the older stuff.


Kirby cleaned his room!!! Well, he did a really thorough cleaning of one end
of it anyway. He's buying a computer with his own money, and has cleaned out
the area where he's going to put it. Vacuumed, brought me stuff to give to
charity, got me to help him find a good place to put the big box of Ninja
Turtle figures, traded his long phone cord for a shorter one (he's decided to
just leave the computer plugged into the phone line and not have a telephone
in there).

This one was NOT my idea. I knew he had room for it without a big clean,
because I had done some big cleaning before Christmas so he'd have room for
the gamecube he didn't know he was getting. His dad put in shelves, and I
organized about half of his stuff (at his request, because he was not
fathoming how it could be done).

So for hours, yesterday, he was cleaning happily, merrily! Having fun!

How cool.

Sandra
